{"tid":2108502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林病月娥今日到慈雲山一所護養院視察","createTime":"2020-07-14T14:49:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T16:16:44.000Z","uid":132380,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"685fb7cea34198b749a060cb82ef5530e6f5b4ca","tid":2108502,"uid":132380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T14:49:46.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥今日（七月十四日）到慈雲山一所護養院，視察政府為安老院舍員工進行2019冠狀病毒病檢測的情況。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥到慈雲山一所護養院，聽取檢測機構──華大基因開設的華昇診斷中心──負責人講解為該院舍約80名員工採集咽拭子樣本進行病毒檢測的安排及程序。今日是政府聯同檢測機構首天開展為安老院舍、殘疾院舍及護養院員工進行病毒檢測，將按所得經驗盡快推展至全港院舍。"},{"pid":"b3d444ba2e6b201ec9a1083ea0be934f98419a25","tid":2108502,"uid":127929,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T14:52:48.000Z","msg":"只求死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e70453944f5fccce3289569972ddd5638bf39c","tid":2108502,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T14:53:14.000Z","msg":"全部DNA送中"},{"pid":"a2bd331cc0bac84a1c140e0512073c98bb864ed9","tid":2108502,"uid":1408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:11:30.000Z","msg":"點解啲廢老唔除口罩打乞痴"},{"pid":"d63719d8cdf6f963459e9807c420ad6aa0739eb1","tid":2108502,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:12:31.000Z","msg":"係咪帶底褲口罩先"},{"pid":"f630fd072f0449eaa82d4cf0b731d8ef0752b2af","tid":2108502,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:13:05.000Z","msg":"快啲中招傳埋比行會局長國安黑警親中狗"},{"pid":"a0092a62463529a42d9f145a4adeb0ee8a4b520f","tid":2108502,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:16:10.000Z","msg":"怪唔知頭先收工番屋企見到咁撚多單邊耳機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b638decec5799989d217f389e9d7a622f2915a","tid":2108502,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:19:11.000Z","msg":"又做show<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" clas